headline: Cummins Inc. Declares Quarterly Common Stock Dividend
summary: COLUMBUS, Ind., February 10, 2026--The Board of Directors of Cummins Inc. (NYSE: CMI) today declared a quarterly common stock cash dividend of 2.00 dollars per share. The dividend is payable on March 5, 2026, to shareholders of record on February 20, 2026.
